# Input
```html
<!-- should generate diagnostics -->
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<style>.card { border: 1px solid; } .title { font-weight: bold; }</style>
<style>.container { max-width: 1200px; } .btn { padding: 8px; }</style>
</head>
<body>
	<!-- .header is not declared in any <style> block -->
	<div class="card header">Single unknown</div>

	<!-- .header and .footer are undeclared -->
	<div class="card header title footer">Multi unknown</div>

	<!-- .header, .footer, .unknown are all undeclared -->
	<div class="header footer unknown">Multi-block unknown</div>

	<!-- .main-content and .unknown-btn are undeclared -->
	<div class="container">
		<main class="main-content">
			<button class="btn unknown-btn">Element types</button>
		</main>
	</div>
</body>
</html>

```

